Localization.Name: 'Arrow' I Missile
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Vanduul
Tracking Signal: Infrared
Size: 1

Commonly known by its military designation, the Arrow is a small infrared strike missile that has become a mainstay of the Vanduul armory.
